I'm a rationalist.

15:22.480 --> 15:26.201
I know I need the best student in the room, to stay in the room

15:26.440 --> 15:28.010
if I want a thought expirement

15:28.120 --> 15:29.770
to yield it's sharpest result.

15:34.760 --> 15:37.331
This is one rude "goodbye", you could've just bought us pastries.

15:37.440 --> 15:40.011
I don't have a problem with an atomic holocaust.

15:40.120 --> 15:41.042
That's the spirit.

15:41.160 --> 15:43.128
We are pioneers of the mind in this classroom

15:43.240 --> 15:45.083
scholars and philosphers

15:45.440 --> 15:47.408
so, this is how it's going to work

15:48.880 --> 15:51.770
you'll each choose at random a card from inside this box

15:51.920 --> 15:53.251
on each card there is a profession

