17:55.080 --> 17:56.081
I'm a published poet.

18:19.840 --> 18:21.649
You would have never have voted him into the bunker

18:23.000 --> 18:24.809
what does a poet bring to the table in the world

18:24.920 --> 18:27.491
we are facing, his skillset was the definition of useless.

