18:48.200 --> 18:50.328
Your still not locking on the conditions of the excercise

18:50.560 --> 18:54.087
you have a brutally short window to calculate, who deserves a slot on your bunker.

18:54.200 --> 18:56.806
Your one tool: logic.

18:56.920 --> 18:57.887
The variables?

18:58.000 --> 19:00.401
Your skill sets as indicated on the cards you chosen.

