Other than that, you are in the thought experiment as you are in real life.

19:05.240 --> 19:07.242
James, name your best characteristic.

19:09.320 --> 19:10.526
I'm a pacifist.

19:10.640 --> 19:12.369
So he is a pacifist in our experiment

19:12.520 --> 19:13.442
it was close call

